snippet.textDisplay: 10 years back I met this young guy at Shangrilla lake, who was told to be a distant relative of mine. 10 years back while having a general conversation he told me about an underground band he is going to start named as KHUMARIYAAN. After 10 years, they’re here! This song (including the lyrics and music) is one of the best CS output till date! Congrats Aamer Shafeq, Khumariyaan, Gul and the beloved Zarsanga <3
